{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "fcf345cb-555f-4af1-9df5-296e85c301f5", "type": 201, "content": {"answer_steps": [], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/fcf345cb-555f-4af1-9df5-296e85c301f5@1.pkg/1772597612803/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597613665", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/fcf345cb-555f-4af1-9df5-296e85c301f5@1.pkg/1772597612803/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597613665"}, "identifier": "fcf345cb-555f-4af1-9df5-296e85c301f5", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">本题考查养成健康的生活方式。</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">D：结合所学知识和材料，可知我们要缓解自己的压力，促进身心健康，对于青少年学生属于健康的生活方式的是心情烦闷时，通过运动来排解，故D符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">A：青少年学生是不可以喝酒的，故A错误；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">BC：经常喝酒、熬夜打游戏、胡乱吃药都是很伤害自己的身体的做法，要适当，故BC说法错误；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">故本题选D。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）&ldquo;世界那么大，我想去看看&rdquo;越来越多的父母选择在暑假带领孩子去看世界，出一次海，翻一座山，访一座城，以此缓解压力，促进身心健康。对于青少年学生，下列属于健康的生活方式的是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）“世界那么大，我想去看看”越来越多的父母选择在暑假带领孩子去看世界，出一次海，翻一座山，访一座城，以此缓解压力，促进身心健康。对于青少年学生，下列属于健康的生活方式的是（   ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/fcf345cb-555f-4af1-9df5-296e85c301f5@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755250440426", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>学习劳累时，喝一杯酒提提神</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>为游戏升级，经常熬夜打游戏</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>每次生病时，胡乱吃药来医治</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>心情烦闷时，通过运动来排解</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）&ldquo;世界那么大，我想去看看&rdquo;越来越多的父母选择在暑假带领孩子去看世界，出一次海，翻一座山，访一座城，以此缓解压力，促进身心健康。对于青少年学生，下列属于健康的生活方式的是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee3